Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管回忆溢满心头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓在干掉的泪痕中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以迎接朋友的方式\N温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此广大的庭院,美丽的新居
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了你\N我不计付出一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?你满不满足?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,我不能这么轻易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天会是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#26 五代愕然!响子醋坛大爆发!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,对不起喔\N突然把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我跟我老公\N相约碰面的时间延后了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,我也很想见你\N所以就跑来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟高中时代一样\N一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样\N有一阵子我很消沈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我有听说,音无老师过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有个孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是带个孩子再婚的话\N应该很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有考虑再婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你总不能一辈子一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是无所谓,你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这么漂亮\N至少有两三个男人在追求你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛,也不是没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我总是无法忘掉过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的个性就是这样\N或许这是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是早点做打算比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间一久的话\N总会忘记死去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是其他的男人不见得\N能等到那个时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在跟一位房客太太\N还有我爸妈说话似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也这么说你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,一天到晚叫我再婚\N听得我耳朵都长茧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊,哪天他们不说了\N你就完蛋了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦率一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再婚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论两年还是三年\N我都会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对象是五代的话\N再婚得等上个四五年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能够爱我这么久吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是早点跟他约定\N等他大学毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到时候我几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生小孩还是30岁前比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点来说,如果是三鹰\N现在马上就能办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌,我在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,没什么好着急的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人都说了愿意等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇,五代居然会打扫房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要来这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说要来煮饭给他吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还说要帮他洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是五代居然说不好意思\N耍酷婉拒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种没出息的男人\N居然也有女人愿意服侍他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事竟然拿来炫耀\N到处去跟人家讲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听到他们讲电话的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛!五代那个人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就让女朋友\N直接帮他煮饭洗衣服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,这样大概可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,这样大概可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?今天是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,是的,我有空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔\N你还特地到外面来等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说\N我想做奶油炖牛肉给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以带了高丽菜,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不要叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小声一点,悄悄进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦,我的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个好登对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好,我是七尾小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶,太大声了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶,我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要跟管理员乱说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N你做了见不得人的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什么见不得人的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看管理员那样\N其实她是个大醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会吃醋啊,太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就叫她帮你做饭洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意说那么大声给我听的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这样气呼呼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个人的交往\N看起来还很清纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁气呼呼的了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代想干嘛,关我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会擦起指甲油?\N有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我今天要跟三鹰约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟三鹰教练有进展了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你以前没说过约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说只是两人见个面\N不是什么约会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然还擦了指甲油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前是那么说的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次来男生的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点脏乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这里的墙壁颜色不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里最近才整修过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直有个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,给我开门\N我知道你在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次再把墙壁弄坏的话\N我不会再忍气吞声了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有老鼠啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是那种可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亲热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…这是情势所逼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的房间,随你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家很害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家会怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我会很困扰的\N真的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修那片墙得花不少钱耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天好漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要去跟三鹰约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是要去约会啊,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他没有开车来接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的车子现在送去车检
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我又不是跟车子约会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,你们也要出门吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想做奶油炖牛肉给他吃\N可是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想请他到我家来吃饭\N向他赔罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有跟她说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是叫人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是这一带没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,竟然选在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么在车站前的\N“珍爱”见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爱犬美容院的二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然选在爱犬美容院…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来,不可以这样,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,裤子弄得脏兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,请进来里面一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代简直像小津江养的小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,三鹰比他可靠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小姐你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在等人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,三鹰比五代自爱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为人长得帅\N就容易被人误会花心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,因为我很怕狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,如果你不嫌弃我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玛,别闹了,快点走开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么不去换奖品呢\N小钢珠都掉满地了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,小钢珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害喔\N我还是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气势真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还送我东西带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我简直就像个小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样厚脸皮交往下去\N真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你的罐头掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要了,送给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很重的样子\N我来帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了\N我不想接受男人的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是和三鹰吵架了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,只是觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约会玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的约会还真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然抱了这么多罐头回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不重吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太舒服的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高兴怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你无关吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了!\N这球飞得很远,真的很远!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中外野手拼命地退后接球\N接得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,飞出去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全垒打!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点应该是这里没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要放我鸽子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得我有做什么\N让她生气的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎竟然被烤肉串给拐走了\N真是条大笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家担心得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它到底跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:23:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“惣一郎不见了?\N回忆是烤肉串的香味”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏时刻回首看到你的身影时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心涌起了一股\N忘却已久的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一场阵雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常在意淋湿的高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前你用那隐藏着\N稚气的侧脸和我交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的话语至今仍能想起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.37,0:25:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就仿佛\N置身电影中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.21,0:25:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你轻声细语地说着\N安静的最后一幕

